<inglise>Final Provisions </inglise>
<eesti>&sect; 34. </eesti>
<inglise>&sect; 34. </inglise>
<eesti>Riigil&otilde;iv </eesti>
<inglise>State fees </inglise>
<eesti>(1) K&auml;esolevas seaduses etten&auml;htud toimingute sooritamise eest v&otilde;etakse riigil&otilde;ivu riigil&otilde;ivuseaduses (RT I 1997, 80, 1344; 2000, 5, 32; 10, 58; 19, 117; 26, 150; 29, 168 ja 169; 39, 237; 49, 300; 54, 346 ja 349; 55, 365; 57, 372 ja 373; 59, 379; 60, &otilde;iend; 78, 498; 84, 534; 92, 597 ja 598) s&auml;testatud m&auml;&auml;rade j&auml;rgi. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) State fees are charged for the performance of acts prescribed in this Act according to the rates provided for in the State Fees Act (RT I 1997, 80, 1344; 2000, 5, 32; 10, 58; 19, 117; 26, 150; 29, 168 and 169; 39, 237; 49, 300; 54, 346 and 349; 55, 365; 57, 372 and 373; 59, 379; 60, correction notice; 78, 498; 84, 534; 92, 597 and 598). </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Riigil&otilde;ivu tasub majutusettev&otilde;tte tunnistuse taotleja v&otilde;i kolmas isik, kes on huvitatud k&auml;esolevas seaduses etten&auml;htud toimingute sooritamisest ja dokumentide v&auml;ljastamisest. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) State fees shall be paid by applicants for certificates of accommodation establishments or third persons who have an interest in the performance of acts and issue of documents prescribed in this Act. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Riigil&otilde;iv loetakse tasutuks, kui selle tasumist t&otilde;endav dokument on saabunud majutusettev&otilde;tte tunnistuse taotlemise korral kohalikule omavalitsusele, j&auml;rgutunnistuse taotlemise korral Majandusministeeriumile. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) A state fee is deemed to be paid if, upon application for the certificate of an accommodation establishment, the local government receives a document certifying payment of the state fee and, upon application for a certificate of category, the Ministry of Economic Affairs receives a document certifying payment of the state fee. </inglise>
