<eesti>Riigil&otilde;ivuseaduse muutmine </eesti>
<inglise>Amendment of State Fees Act </inglise>
<eesti>Riigil&otilde;ivuseaduse (RT I 1997, 80, 1344; 2000, 5, 32; 10, 58; 19, 117; 26, 150; 29, 168 ja 169; 39, 237; 49, 300; 54, 346 ja 349; 55, 365; 57, 372 ja 373; 59, 379; 60, &otilde;iend; 78, 498; 84, 534; 92, 597 ja 598) &sect; 183 t&auml;iendatakse l&otilde;igetega 3 (16) -3 (18) j&auml;rgmises s&otilde;nastuses: </eesti>
<inglise>Section 183 of the State Fees Act (RT I 1997, 80, 1344; 2000, 5, 32; 316, 58; 19, 117; 26, 150; 29, 168 and 169; 39, 237; 49, 300; 54, 346 and 349; 55, 365, 57, 372 and 373, 59, 379; 60, correction notice; 78, 498; 84, 534; 92, 597 and 598) is amended by adding subsections (3 (16)) -(3 (18)) worded as follows: </inglise>
<eesti>"(3 (16)) Majutusettev&otilde;tte tunnistuse v&auml;ljastamise eest tasutakse riigil&otilde;ivu 100 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>"(3 (16)) A state fee of 100 kroons is charged for the issue of the certificate of an accommodation establishment. </inglise>
<eesti>(3 (17)) J&auml;rgutunnistuse v&auml;ljastamise eest tasutakse riigil&otilde;ivu kuni 50 numbritoaga majutusettev&otilde;tte korral: </eesti>
<inglise>(3 (17)) In the case of accommodation establishments with up to fifty rooms, a state fee is charged in the following amounts for the issue of a certificate of category: </inglise>
<eesti>1) &uuml;het&auml;rnihotelli j&auml;rgu taotlemisel 300 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>1) 300 kroons upon application for the category of a one star hotel; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kahet&auml;rnihotelli j&auml;rgu taotlemisel 400 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>2) 400 kroons upon application for the category of a two star hotel; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kolmet&auml;rnihotelli j&auml;rgu taotlemisel 700 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>3) 700 kroons upon application for the category of a three star hotel; </inglise>
<eesti>4) neljat&auml;rnihotelli j&auml;rgu taotlemisel 900 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>4) 900 kroons upon application for the category of a four star hotel; </inglise>
<eesti>5) viiet&auml;rnihotelli j&auml;rgu taotlemisel 1000 krooni. </eesti>
<inglise>5) 1000 kroons upon application for the category of a five star hotel. </inglise>
<eesti>(3 (18)) J&auml;rgutunnistuse v&auml;ljastamise eest tasutakse riigil&otilde;ivu &uuml;le 50 numbritoaga majutusettev&otilde;tte korral: </eesti>
<inglise>(3 (18)) In the case of accommodation establishments with more than fifty rooms, a state fee is charged in the following amounts for the issue of a certificate of category: </inglise>
<eesti>1) &uuml;het&auml;rnihotelli j&auml;rgu taotlemisel 500 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>1) 500 kroons upon application for the category of a one star hotel; </inglise>
<eesti>2) kahet&auml;rnihotelli j&auml;rgu taotlemisel 600 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>2) 600 kroons upon application for the category of a two star hotel; </inglise>
<eesti>3) kolmet&auml;rnihotelli j&auml;rgu taotlemisel 900 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>3) 900 kroons upon application for the category of a three star hotel; </inglise>
<eesti>4) neljat&auml;rnihotelli j&auml;rgu taotlemisel 1100 krooni; </eesti>
<inglise>4) 1100 kroons upon application for the category of a four star hotel; </inglise>
<eesti>5) viiet&auml;rnihotelli j&auml;rgu taotlemisel 1300 krooni." </eesti>
<inglise>5) 1300 kroons upon application for the category of a five star hotel." </inglise>
