<eesti>&Uuml;leminekus&auml;tted </eesti>
<inglise>Transitional provisions </inglise>
<eesti>(1) Ettev&otilde;tja, kellele on enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist majandusministri poolt turismialaseks ettev&otilde;tluseks v&auml;ljastatud tegevuslitsents, mille kehtivuse t&auml;htaeg l&otilde;peb p&auml;rast 2001. aasta 1. m&auml;rtsi, v&otilde;ib pakkuda ja osutada reisiteenuseid tegevuslitsentsil m&auml;rgitud t&auml;htp&auml;eva saabumiseni, kuid mitte kauem kui 2001. aasta 1. juulini. </eesti>
<inglise>(1) Undertakings which are issued, prior to the entry into force of this Act, activity licences for provision of tourism services by the Minister of Economic Affairs the term of validity of which expires after 1 March 2001 may offer and provide travel services until the due date indicated on the activity licence but not longer than until 1 July 2001. </inglise>
<eesti>(2) Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist kehtinud &otilde;igusakte j&auml;rgides v&auml;ljastatud majutusettev&otilde;tte tunnistus kehtib sellel m&auml;rgitud t&auml;htp&auml;eva saabumiseni, kuid mitte kauem kui 2002. aasta 1. jaanuarini. </eesti>
<inglise>(2) Certificates of accommodation establishments issued pursuant to legislation in force prior to the entry into force of this Act shall be valid until the due date indicated on the certificate but not longer than 1 January 2002. </inglise>
<eesti>(3) Enne k&auml;esoleva seaduse j&otilde;ustumist kehtinud &otilde;igusakte j&auml;rgides v&auml;ljastatud tunnistus hotellile omistatud kategooria kohta, mille kehtivuse t&auml;htaeg l&otilde;peb p&auml;rast 2001. aasta 1. m&auml;rtsi, kehtib sellel m&auml;rgitud t&auml;htp&auml;eva saabumiseni, kuid mitte kauem kui 2002. aasta 1. jaanuarini. </eesti>
<inglise>(3) Certificates of categories assigned to hotels issued pursuant to legislation in force prior to the entry into force of this Act and the term of validity of which expires after 1 March 2001 shall be valid until the due date indicated on the certificate but not longer than until 1 January 2002. </inglise>
<eesti>(4) Ettev&otilde;tja, kellele on v&auml;ljastatud k&auml;esoleva paragrahvi l&otilde;ikes 1 nimetatud tegevuslitsents, ei pea sellise tegevuslitsentsi kehtivuse ajal omama k&auml;esoleva seaduse &sect;-s 15 s&auml;testatud tagatist. </eesti>
<inglise>(4) Undertakings which are issued activity licences specified in subsection (1) of this section are not required to hold a security provided for in &sect; 15 of this Act during the term of validity of such activity licence. </inglise>
